content: /*<![CDATA[*/ $('#title').html($('meta[name=map-description]').attr('content')); /*]]>*/ Support for moving user-reported emails to Junk Email folder in Cloud Email and Collaboration Protection June 21, 2024—To help automatically removing emails from end users' inboxes that they have reported as spam or phishing through the Cloud Email and Collaboration Protection add-in for Outlook, Cloud Email and Collaboration Protection now provides the option to move these emails to the end users' Junk Email folder.
